                    <p xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">
                        puḻaṟkōṭṭattu nāyaṟu-nāṭṭu-t tiru-k-kāṭṭu-p-paḷḷi-p pañcavaram ĀIrakkā
